<bibRefCitation author="O'Shaughnessy, W. B." box="[1004,1314,1328,1351]" pageId="2" pageNumber="59" refId="ref4796" refString="O'Shaughnessy, W. B. (1841) The Bengal dispensatory and pharmacopoeia chiefly compiled from the works of Roxburgh, Wallich, Ainslie, Wight and Arnot, Royle, Pereira, Lindley, Richard, and Fee, and including the results of numerous special experiments. Bishop's College Press, Calcutta." type="book" year="1841">O’Shaughnessy (1841: 505)</bibRefCitation>
